data.description: Charming home in quaint neighborhood of Blanco River Village. Tree lined street and wrap around porch greets you into this 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath. Featured on main level is an eat in Kitchen, spacious Dining and Living room with gas starter fireplace, half bath, Office or flex room with exterior door that leads you to the detached Garage and fenced in backyard.  All bedrooms upstairs to include primary main suite complete with ensuite bathroom and a private balcony to sit back and relax on. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, and easy access to IH 35.
